Package: ratetest
Title: Test if the rate of a event in two groups is different
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Luca",
           family = "Vedovelli",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lucavd@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4847-2333"))
Description: This package has a single function named `rate_test()` that does a single thing: test the rate of an event is significantly different between two groups, returning a p-value and 95% calculated with and exact poisson distribution.
